  "text": [
    "Now that I know",
    "That passion warms little",
    "Of flesh in the mold,",
    "And treasure is brittle,",
    "I\u2019ll lie here and learn",
    "How, over their ground,",
    "Trees make a long shadow",
    "And a light sound."
